<text id="APB0133T">

<body>
<div1 type="summary">
<p>Note payable in lead.</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">

<p><location_mentioned>Lexington </location_mentioned><date_mentioned n="12-10-1807">10th Decr 1807</date_mentioned></p>
<p>1720lbs Bar Lead</p>

<p>Three months after date, I promise to pay <person_mentioned>Lewis Sanders</person_mentioned> or order,
Seventeen hundred and Twenty pounds of Small bar Lead, for value
Received to be delivered in <location_mentioned>Lexington Kentucky</location_mentioned>—</p>

<p>$72                                                 Moses Austin & Co    [Rubric]</p>

<p>Received of <person_mentioned>Charles Carr</person_mentioned> the Above note in full <date_mentioned n="07-06-1808">July 6 1808</date_mentioned></p>

<p><person_mentioned>L. V. Hawkins</person_mentioned>
for <person_mentioned>Lewis Sanders</person_mentioned></p>
<p>Recd. <date_mentioned n="04-15-1808">15th Apr.</date_mentioned> 1635lbs bar Lead</p>
<p>[Endorsed]   Note N° 2</p>
<p><person_mentioned>Moses Austin</person_mentioned> <date_mentioned n="12-10-1807">10th Decm. 1807</date_mentioned></p>
<p>Due <date_mentioned n="03-10-1808">10th March 1808</date_mentioned></p>
</div1>
